{"tid":2492713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以 Main 取代 Master 10 月生效，Github 移除涉歧視術語","createTime":"2021-04-17T10:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T10:35:25.000Z","uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7c35a84c8e501a23bc7af6520f380fe98387ea25","tid":2492713,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"在一片反種族歧視浪潮下，為了政治正確，今年 6 月中 GitHub 宣布將標示主分支的術語「Master」改為「Main」，避免出現隱含主人和奴隸的意思。當時 GitHub 曾在 Nat Friedman 指術語「Master」與美國黑奴歷史有關，要求科技界以其他詞語取代，對多元社會更友善。"},{"pid":"a7af1d5dac337798f44c6f84a5e422673346782e","tid":2492713,"uid":155295,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:30:25.000Z","msg":"MasterCard 要改名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09223e147a5c7087a6086e1736ccaa2dbd161bd0","tid":2492713,"uid":249761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:31:32.000Z","msg":"Whitelist?<br />\nBlacklist?<br />\nHistory?<br />\nSlave?"},{"pid":"7920e36a53d678c2b065ea29c679ed49793d5278","tid":2492713,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7af1d5dac337798f44c6f84a5e422673346782e","tid":2492713,"uid":155295,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:30:25.000Z","msg":"MasterCard 要改名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:32:14.000Z","msg":"Maincard"},{"pid":"cf9899e8b3b826c2e11ac5a66f04895567381cbb","tid":2492713,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:34:02.000Z","msg":"master Yi<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDoubt is the greatest enemy <br />\nAnger gives motivation without purpose"},{"pid":"3af8a56db1bbb2fa91696192d2496bbd594d7b83","tid":2492713,"uid":147467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09223e147a5c7087a6086e1736ccaa2dbd161bd0","tid":2492713,"uid":249761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"r